    <ol class="c3 lst-kix_lxx37dmpc6yq-0 start" start="1">
      <li class="c9 c15 li-bullet-0">
        <h3 id="h.v6mxtjqlo54s" style="display:inline"><span class="c13">Earning Points from Purchases</span></h3>
      </li>
    </ol>
    <p class="c5"><span>For every </span><span class="c6">IDR 1,000</span><span>&nbsp;spent on your purchase, you will earn </span><span class="c6">1 point</span><span class="c1">. This means that every time you make a purchase, the amount you spend directly translates into points that accumulate in your account.</span></p>
