        <h3 id="h.3wm6q48xgj0k" style="display:inline"><span class="c13">Earning Points by Reviewing Products</span></h3>
      </li>
    </ol>
    <p class="c8"><span>We encourage customers to share their experiences with our products. After purchasing any product, you have the option to leave a </span><span>review</span><span>. By doing so, you will earn an additional </span><span class="c6">150 points</span><span class="c1">&nbsp;as a reward.</span></p>
