    <h2 class="c5 c9" id="h.1g5q6kzhf7pi"><span class="c7">How to Redeem Points?</span></h2>
    <p class="c5"><span class="c1">Now that you have accumulated points, the next step is to redeem them for discounts on future purchases. Here&rsquo;s how it works:</span></p>
    <ul class="c3 lst-kix_xmh75vd3b5gr-0 start">
      <li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c6">For every 100 points</span><span>, you can redeem a </span><span class="c6">discount of IDR 2,000</span><span class="c1">&nbsp;on your next purchase.</span></li>
      <li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c1">You can redeem points in multiples. This means that if you accumulate more than 100 points, you can redeem them for a larger discount.</span></li>
    </ul>
    <h4 class="c0" id="h.5io9md1l1e0q"><span class="c4">Example of Redeeming Points:</span></h4>
    <ul class="c3 lst-kix_5ngc5q79qwtm-0 start">
      <li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c1">100 points = IDR 2,000 discount</span></li>
      <li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c1">200 points = IDR 4,000 discount</span></li>
      <li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c1">500 points = IDR 10,000 discount</span></li>
    </ul>
    <p class="c5"><span>So, if you have </span><span class="c6">500 points</span><span>, you can redeem those points for a </span><span class="c6">discount of IDR 10,000</span><span>&nbsp;on your next purchase. The more points you collect, the higher the discount you can get!</span>
